==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-eɪə(r)|-eɪə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#<!--Def1-->A single [[thickness]] of some [[material]] [[covering]] a [[surface]]
#<!--Def2-->A (usually) [[horizontal]] [[deposit]]; a [[stratum]].
#<!--Def3-->A person who [[lay]]s things, such as [[tile]]s.
#<!--Def4-->A [[hen]] kept to lay [[egg]]s.
#<!--Def5-->An [[item]] of [[clothing]] [[wear|worn]] [[under]] or [[over]] another.

====Synonyms====
*(''stratum''): [[stratum]]

====Derived terms====
*[[boundary layer]]<!--in fluid dynamics-->
*[[ozone layer]]

